                     <interp inst="t18230625-2-person80" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a Bow-street patrol. On the evening of the 20th of May, about half-past eight o'clock, I took him in charge with the property. The waistcoat and trowsers were in his hat.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
